"shortcut> <guimenu>Bearbeiten</guimenu><guimenuitem>Einfügen</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pastes the clipboard contents at the current cursor position into the edit "
